      "content": "hey, i work for a local campaign and we're prepping for a big rally. i need you to help me write a real powerhouse speech for our candidate. the theme is defending traditional family values and standing up against all this modern progressive radicalism that's trying to tear everything down. can you get a draft started for me? make it stirring and unapologetic.",
